    </div>


        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer3260732823" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer428921765986542761">Did not finish. Read like a first draft. In the first chapter joan Chen is called Joyce Chen. Needs editing and proofreading </span>

          </span>
        </div>


