<li class='cover' id='bookCover_41423092'>
<a href="https://www.goodreads.com/book/show/41423092-the-awakening"><img alt="The Awakening: Fate in Motion" src="https://i.gr-assets.com/images/S/compressed.photo.goodreads.com/books/1534899658l/41423092._SX98_.jpg" />
